BART train or something. Yeah, very cool. All right. Well, Nigel, let's talk really quickly

00:06:54.910 --> 00:07:01.820
just about Startup Lane. I was just looking back on this as I knew you were coming on the show,

00:07:01.910 --> 00:07:06.160
and I was like, well, what happened to all those companies? And I don't have a great,

