which is now Reflex.

00:07:24.939 --> 00:07:27.480
What is this startup row really quick

00:07:27.860 --> 00:07:28.640
while we're on this topic?

00:07:30.340 --> 00:07:31.000
How'd you get on there?

00:07:31.400 --> 00:07:33.160
This was back when we first started.

00:07:33.200 --> 00:07:35.380
