00:22:41.230 --> 00:22:44.160
So we have a built-in ORM similar to Django.

00:22:44.560 --> 00:22:48.020
It's nothing but a kind of light wrapper around SQLAlchemy,

00:22:49.480 --> 00:22:51.520
but kind of hooked up more to Reflex.

