for any SQL database because of the SQLAlchemy

00:23:04.200 --> 00:23:04.780
like tight integration.

00:23:05.880 --> 00:23:07.360
So when you start Reflex,

00:23:07.400 --> 00:23:09.860
you have a built-in SQLite database that gets,

00:23:10.480 --> 00:23:12.520
any app that wants it, it's there for you.

00:23:12.520 --> 00:23:13.820
