00:26:43.660 --> 00:26:45.980
I think we're gonna chat about it maybe a bit later,

00:26:46.540 --> 00:26:48.120
but our goal, like right now,

00:26:48.320 --> 00:26:52.200
A big part of it is making, okay, you can write your UI in Python, right?

00:26:52.450 --> 00:26:54.040
So it's making that part of it more accessible.

00:26:54.960 --> 00:26:58.320
But our goal is not necessarily, you know, to stop at Python.

00:26:58.580 --> 00:27:01.380
Our goal is just to make it easy for someone with an idea to build a web app.

00:27:01.960 --> 00:27:07.180
So along those lines, like, as we started, a lot of the positive comments people have said is,

00:27:07.270 --> 00:27:09.440
okay, now I can, you know, one language, one framework.

