00:29:34.550 --> 00:29:37.240
How do I actually make this nice thing actually practical?

00:29:38.140 --> 00:29:41.540
So I think that's kind of the approach we're trying to do is like once if we have these

00:29:41.640 --> 00:29:43.620
AI features, it's not just an AI to build.

00:29:44.220 --> 00:29:48.020
