00:29:48.140 --> 00:29:48.440
with it.

00:29:49.080 --> 00:29:53.720
So it's like Python we see as great in this, in this thing as like an intermediate language

00:29:54.000 --> 00:29:57.360
with which both AI can kind of write to and a developer can actually understand in the

00:29:57.420 --> 00:30:01.700
end, compared to an AI outputting a bunch of react code, which would be really hard for

