00:56:12.590 --> 00:56:13.680
this into an existing app?

00:56:14.000 --> 00:56:17.740
Like it's good at building brand new stuff, but how do I like update an existing app?

00:56:18.300 --> 00:56:23.700
So on this front, we're building a local AI toolbar, which has a lot of these agentic features

00:56:23.960 --> 00:56:25.940
around Reflex, but on your local.

00:56:26.660 --> 00:56:30.360
So for example, the features we have there are you can click a button and say, when I

00:56:30.480 --> 00:56:34.640
click the button, do this or click a text and say change, like, you know, put a form

00:56:34.780 --> 00:56:35.260
