00:56:35.660 --> 00:56:49.200
And the big idea there, I think this is a good first start, but I think in the long run, I'd see the toolbar as being this way where the AI and the developer kind of integrate together with Python as the common language.

00:56:49.940 --> 00:56:56.080
So for crazy stuff that you don't want to deal with, like make a form that works in mobile view, et cetera, the AI can handle a lot of this.

00:56:56.680 --> 00:57:02.120
