00:57:14.640 --> 00:57:17.160
How do I actually make it hook up with my clicks,

00:57:17.340 --> 00:57:18.500
hook up with my different data?

00:57:19.680 --> 00:57:21.640
So that's a big part of what we're trying to bring

00:57:21.780 --> 00:57:22.520
to the local environment.

00:57:23.420 --> 00:57:24.140
Yeah, that's cool.

00:57:24.160 --> 00:57:27.980
And so this thing will generate a visual look and feel thing,

00:57:27.980 --> 00:57:29.100
and you actually go show the code.

